{"tid":693614,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"勒邦占士：「對我而言，首3場只是試探性的比賽。」","createTime":"2018-06-07T15:08:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T06:29:26.000Z","uid":28938,"like":166,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"813a81e8c37f24384f9838cd5a60f1997887fb72","tid":693614,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:08:53.000Z","msg":"騎士以102-110不敵勇士。此役過後，騎士在季後總決賽中以0-3落後勇士。賽後騎士前鋒勒邦占士接受媒體採訪，對反勝充滿了信心。<br />\n<br />\n占士說道：「對我而言，首3場只是試探性的比賽。關於他們應對我的方式，我已完全了解，我也差不多搞清自己在進入Game 4時該怎麼做了。」<br />\n<br />\n占士續預言道：「他們痛宰了我們三場，毫不留情，我們再反勝他們四場，像利物浦於2005年歐冠盃決賽反勝AC米蘭一樣。」<br />\n<br />\nNineup報記者提醒：「但上個月利物浦在決賽敗給皇馬了。」<br />\n<br />\n占士反駁道：「利物浦還有Game 2，英超亞洲挑戰盃！他媽的難道不捧盃在望嗎？」"},{"pid":"fdb2fb7383476869853db9467aaa7007079db348","tid":693614,"uid":67896,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:09:31.000Z","msg":"9up報！！！！"},{"pid":"9f9b77997189bd4bfca958a4d304b5e20de7cda8","tid":693614,"uid":56240,"like":13,"dislike":5,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:10:01.000Z","msg":"如果真係0-3反CUP到<br />\n超越MJ啦"},{"pid":"6bc5be5fed222e520d92349283d26331dee02324","tid":693614,"uid":137764,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:10:37.000Z","msg":"冇他媽的同no!no!no!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d77286d425f772b25870ca94d2899d6eda3c3adc","tid":693614,"uid":4492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:10:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e84bc3cca0a7e294c7d54beaaca76c7b7cd55430","tid":693614,"uid":28938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fdb2fb7383476869853db9467aaa7007079db348","tid":693614,"uid":67896,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:09:31.000Z","msg":"9up報！！！！"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:17:07.000Z","msg":"最近做完幾個IPO,返工無咁忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/